  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Prerequisites: Str 25, rage 5/day.\nBenefit: Any weapon the character wields while in a rage is treated as a thundering weapon. The DC of the Fortitude save to resist deafness is equal to 10 + 1/2 the character's level. This ability does not stack with similar abilities.",
